   <property name="text">
    <string>Remote Output sends track metadata to a remote What's Now Playing instance.
Enable auto-discover to find services automatically. Click "Scan for servers" to find instances on your local network and select one from the list.
If multiple instances are found, you must select one from the list to save it as your target.
The remote server must be running with the webserver enabled.</string>
